## ⚙️ How It Works

```
GitHub Actions (every 4h)
        │
        ▼
python sectoral_news_dashboard.py
        │   fetches RSS feeds (ET, Mint, Google News)
        │   filters by sector keywords
        │   generates sectoral_news_dashboard.html
        ▼
GitHub Pages → index.html (live site)
```

- **No API key required** — uses public RSS feeds
- **Keyword filtering** — only sector-relevant articles shown per tab
- **Auto-refreshes** every 4 hours via GitHub Actions cron

